<h1>Definition of the Target Audience & Scientific Projects</h1>

<div class="section">

  <p>
    Scientific research is a progressive activity that begins at the undergraduate level,
    continues through Master's studies, and extends to PhD and postdoctoral research.
  </p>

  <p>
    Each stage corresponds to increasing scientific responsibility, autonomy, and expected impact.
  </p>

</div>

<div class="section">

  <h2>Funding Levels</h2>

  <div class="level-card">
    <div class="level-title">Bolsa de Iniciação à Investigação (BII)</div>
    <div class="amount">
      €701.12 – €1,090.98 / month<br>
      €8,413.44 – €13,091.76 / year
    </div>
    Introductory research training at undergraduate level.
  </div>

  <div class="level-card">
    <div class="level-title">Bolsa de Investigação (BI) – Non-degree students / Graduates</div>
    <div class="amount">
      €1,090.98 – €1,852.52 / month<br>
      €13,091.76 – €22,230.24 / year
    </div>
    Development of advanced research skills, potentially leading to publications.
  </div>

  <div class="level-card">
    <div class="level-title">Bolsa de Investigação (BI) – Master’s level</div>
    <div class="amount">
      €1,090.98 – €1,852.52 / month<br>
      €13,091.76 – €22,230.24 / year
    </div>
    Research training within Master's studies.
  </div>

  <div class="level-card">
    <div class="level-title">Bolsa de Investigação (BI) – Doctoral level</div>
    <div class="amount">
      €1,359.64 – €2,168.65 / month<br>
      €16,315.68 – €26,023.80 / year
    </div>
    Full-time original research leading to a PhD thesis.
  </div>

  <div class="level-card">
    <div class="level-title">Bolsa de Investigação Pós-Doutoral (BIPD)</div>
    <div class="amount">
      €1,901.00 – €2,712.03 / month<br>
      €22,812.00 – €32,544.36 / year
    </div>
    Independent research with increasing scientific autonomy.
  </div>

</div>

<div class="section">

  <h2>Funding Policy</h2>

  <div class="note-box">
    <p>
      Funding is exclusively dedicated to human research activity and scientific output.
      No material costs (equipment, hardware, etc.) are included.
    </p>

    <p>Eligible expenses include:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Research fellowships and contracts</li>
      <li>Conference participation (registration, travel, accommodation)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    All research activities will be conducted at the University of Lisbon.
  </p>

</div>

</body>
